(1014,113,'Recuperar','',6);
INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES
(10,9,'<p>This survey assesses your organization&rsquo;s compliance with the <strong>NIS2</strong> Directive&rsquo;s risk management requirements.</p>\r\n<p>This survey is organized into <strong>nine sections</strong> (pages) covering key risk management areas under the NIS2 Directive. Each page presents multiple-choice question(s) related to that topic. If any answer is incorrect (indicating non-compliance), a Recommendation is provided to guide you on improving compliance. This recommendation will be available in the dashboard section.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The survey is designed for large organizations but is also applicable to SMEs and public sector entities.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em data-end=\"844\" data-start=\"676\">(NIS2 requires measures appropriate to the entity&rsquo;s size, risk exposure, and impact, so answer according to your context.)</em></strong></p>'),
(47,91,'<p>Do you have <strong>formal</strong>, <strong>documented</strong> policies for cybersecurity risk analysis?</p>'),
(52,96,'<p>Do you have a documented incident response plan that defines roles, responsibilities, and procedures for handling cybersecurity incidents?</p>'),
(54,97,'<p>Does your organization have a formal business continuity and disaster recovery plan that includes strategies for cyber incidents?</p>'),
(56,91,'<p>Are these policies <strong>regularly</strong> reviewed and updated to address evolving threats?</p>'),
(57,96,'<p>Which of the following measures has your organization implemented to detect and respond to security incidents? (Select one that applies)</p>'),
(58,97,'<p>Are your backup and recovery procedures regularly tested to ensure data and system restoration in case of an incident?</p>'),
(59,98,'<p>Do you evaluate the cybersecurity posture of your key suppliers and service providers?</p>'),
(60,98,'<p>Are cybersecurity requirements (e.g., compliance with specific security standards, incident reporting obligations) included in contracts with your suppliers?</p>'),
(61,98,'<p>Do you periodically review and update your supply chain risk assessments to address emerging threats?&nbsp;</p>'),
(62,100,'<p>Which secure development and maintenance practices has your organization adopted for its networks and information systems? (Select one that applies)</p>'),
(63,101,'<p>How do you evaluate the effectiveness of your cybersecurity risk management measures? (Select all that apply)</p>'),
(64,101,'<p>Do you engage external audits or third-party assessments to validate the effectiveness of your cybersecurity measures?</p>'),
(65,102,'<p>Which of the following basic cyber hygiene practices are implemented in your organization? (Select all that apply)</p>'),
(66,102,'<p>Do you provide regular cybersecurity training to all employees?</p>'),
(67,103,'<p>Do you implement encryption to protect sensitive data both in transit and at rest?</p>'),
(68,103,'<p>Are internal communications and remote access channels secured using encryption (e.g., secure email, VPNs, encrypted messaging)?</p>'),
(70,104,'<p>Do you have formal onboarding and offboarding procedures to manage user accounts, ensuring that access rights are granted and revoked appropriately?</p>'),
(71,104,'<p>Does your organization enforce access control policies (such as least-privilege access) and maintain an updated inventory of assets and user accounts?</p>'),
(72,104,'<p>Is Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) required for access to critical systems and sensitive data?</p>'),
(73,91,'<p>How frequently does your organization conduct formal cybersecurity risk assessments?</p>'),
(74,91,'<p>Are all relevant stakeholders (e.g., IT, management, and end-users) adequately <strong>informed</strong> and <strong>trained</strong> on the cybersecurity risk policies?</p>'),
(75,101,'<p>How frequently are your security metrics and controls reviewed and updated?</p>'),
(76,101,'<p>Do you maintain a comprehensive, documented log of all security assessments, test results, and follow-up actions?</p>'),
(77,102,'<p>How often is cybersecurity awareness training provided to employees?</p>'),
(78,102,'<p>Do you have a formal evaluation process to measure the effectiveness of your cybersecurity training programs?</p>'),
(80,103,'<p>How frequently are user access rights and privileges reviewed to ensure they adhere to the principle of least privilege?</p>'),
(81,103,'<p>Do you conduct periodic background checks and provide specialized security training for employees in sensitive or privileged roles?</p>'),
(82,96,'<p>How frequently does your organization conduct formal cybersecurity risk assessments?</p>'),
(83,96,'<p>Are all relevant stakeholders (e.g., IT, management, and end-users) adequately informed and trained on the cybersecurity risk policies?</p>'),
(84,97,'<p>How frequently are your business continuity and disaster recovery plans tested?</p>'),
(85,97,'<p>Is there a dedicated crisis management team with clearly defined roles and responsibilities to handle cybersecurity incidents that affect business continuity?</p>'),
(86,100,'<p>Do you conduct regular security testing&mdash;such as code reviews, penetration tests, or static code analysis&mdash;during the system development process?</p>'),
(300,200,'<p>Does your organization have a documented process for obtaining explicit consent for data collection?</p>'),
(301,200,'<p>Are data subjects provided with clear and comprehensive information about the purpose and scope of data collection at the time of consent?</p>'),
(302,200,'<p>Is consent recorded and stored securely for future reference and audit purposes?</p>'),
(303,201,'Do you have technical and organizational measures in place to ensure the integrity and confidentiality of personal data during processing?'),
(304,201,'Are access controls and authentication mechanisms regularly reviewed and updated to prevent unauthorized access?'),
(305,201,'Is personal data processed only for legitimate purposes in accordance with documented procedures?'),
(306,202,'Does your organization have procedures that allow data subjects to access, rectify, or erase their personal data upon request?'),
(307,202,'Are there mechanisms in place to facilitate data portability and allow data subjects to object to certain processing activities?'),
(308,202,'Is there a process to provide data subjects with information about data processing activities in a timely manner?'),
(309,203,'Does your organization have an incident response plan that includes procedures for notifying supervisory authorities within 72 hours of a data breach?'),
(310,203,'Are breach notifications communicated to affected data subjects in a clear and timely manner?'),
(311,203,'Is there regular training and review of breach notification procedures for relevant staff?'),
(322,200,'How often is the consent mechanism reviewed to incorporate changes in legal requirements?'),
(323,201,'Do you conduct regular penetration testing to evaluate the effectiveness of your security measures?'),
(324,202,'Are data subject requests resolved within the legally mandated timeframe?'),
(325,203,'Is there a designated breach response team that meets periodically to review and update incident response protocols?'),
(327,214,'Do you have a documented data retention policy that defines the retention period for different categories of personal data?'),
(328,214,'Is personal data regularly reviewed and deleted when no longer necessary for the purpose it was collected?'),
(329,215,'Do you have contracts in place with third parties that clearly define data protection obligations?'),
(330,215,'Are international transfers of personal data conducted in compliance with GDPR requirements, such as using standard contractual clauses or approved mechanisms?'),
(331,217,'<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"116\">This survey assesses your organization&rsquo;s compliance with the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong> requirements.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"116\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"477\">This survey is organized into multiple sections (pages) covering key data protection areas under GDPR. Each page presents multiple-choice question(s) related to that topic. If any answer is incorrect (indicating non-compliance), a Recommendation is provided to guide you on improving compliance. This recommendation will be available in the <strong>dashboard section</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"477\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"584\">The survey is designed for large organizations but is also applicable to SMEs and public sector entities.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"584\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"730\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">(GDPR requires measures appropriate to the entity&rsquo;s data processing operations, risk exposure, and impact, so answer according to your context.)</p>'),
(344,221,'<p>This survey assesses your organization&rsquo;s compliance with the <strong>NIS2</strong> Incident Notification requirements.</p>\r\n<p>This survey is organized into <strong>five sections</strong> (pages) covering key risk management areas under the NIS2 Directive. Each page presents multiple-choice question(s) related to that topic. If any answer is incorrect (indicating non-compliance), a Recommendation is provided to guide you on improving compliance. This recommendation will be available in the dashboard section.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The survey is designed for large organizations but is also applicable to SMEs and public sector entities.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em data-end=\"844\" data-start=\"676\">(NIS2 requires measures appropriate to the entity&rsquo;s size, risk exposure, and impact, so answer according to your context.)</em></strong></p>'),
(345,222,'Do you have an automated incident detection system that triggers immediate alerts when unusual activity is detected?'),
(346,222,'Are incidents verified by a dedicated incident response team within the first 15 minutes of detection?'),
(347,222,'Is there a predefined protocol for initiating incident notifications to the relevant teams once an incident is detected?'),
(348,222,'Are automated alert systems integrated with your incident management platform to facilitate immediate action?'),
(349,223,'Are internal stakeholders immediately notified through an established communication channel when an incident is detected?'),
(350,223,'Is there a clear escalation path for incidents that require senior management involvement?'),
(351,223,'Are roles and responsibilities clearly defined for each team member involved in incident response?'),
(352,223,'Is there a dedicated internal incident management portal to centralize communication among stakeholders?'),
(353,224,'Do you have procedures to notify external stakeholders (e.g., regulators, clients, partners) within the required regulatory timelines?'),
(354,224,'Are external notifications reviewed for clarity, consistency, and legal compliance before they are sent?'),
(355,224,'Is there a dedicated communication team responsible for handling external incident notifications?'),
(356,224,'Do you have pre-approved templates for external communication to ensure consistency during incident notifications?'),
(357,225,'Do you conduct a formal post-incident review to assess the effectiveness of your notification and communication processes?'),
(358,225,'Are lessons learned from past incidents used to update and improve your incident notification protocols?'),
(359,225,'Is feedback from both internal and external stakeholders on the incident communication process systematically collected and acted upon?'),
(360,225,'Are incident review meetings scheduled immediately after major incidents to capture lessons learned?'),
(361,226,'Does your organization have a formal process for post-incident analysis to identify root causes and implement corrective actions?'),
(362,226,'Are lessons learned from each incident formally documented and reviewed to update incident response and recovery plans?'),
(363,226,'Is there a follow-up mechanism to ensure that corrective actions identified during post-incident reviews are implemented effectively?'),
(364,226,'Does your organization conduct periodic audits of post-incident recovery processes to assess their effectiveness and compliance with internal standards?'),
(365,227,'<p>Choose your level</p>'),
(366,228,'<p>Level Advanced</p>'),
(367,228,'<p>Level Inter</p>'),
(495,229,'<div class=\"mb-6\">\r\n<div class=\"mb-4 bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-4\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"148\">Este inqu&eacute;rito avalia o n&iacute;vel de conformidade da sua organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de acordo com o <strong>Quadro Nacional de Refer&ecirc;ncia para a Ciberseguran&ccedil;a (QNRCS).</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"587\">Este inqu&eacute;rito est&aacute; organizado em <strong>5 sec&ccedil;&otilde;es</strong> (p&aacute;ginas) que abrangem os 5 dom&iacute;nios chave, conforme o QNRCS. Cada p&aacute;gina apresenta perguntas de escolha m&uacute;ltipla. Dado que este inqu&eacute;rito &eacute; <strong>nivelado</strong>, poder&aacute; de seguida escolher o n&iacute;vel de conformidade pretendido.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"587\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"587\">Caso a resposta n&atilde;o esteja em comformidade com o n&iacute;vel escolhido, ser&aacute; fornecida uma recomenda&ccedil;&atilde;o para o orientar na melhoria da conformidade, a qual estar&aacute; dispon&iacute;vel na sec&ccedil;&atilde;o do <strong><em>Dashboard</em></strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"587\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"704\">O inqu&eacute;rito foi concebido para pequenas e m&eacute;dias empresas (PMEs), mas &eacute; igualmente aplic&aacute;vel a grandes entidades e entidades do setor p&uacute;blico.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"704\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"894\">(O Quadro Nacional de Refer&ecirc;ncia para a Ciberseguran&ccedil;a exige medidas apropriadas ao tamanho da entidade, &agrave; exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o ao risco e ao seu impacto, pelo que deve responder de acordo com o seu contexto.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
